    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Paying the Bill</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>David Cantor and Kelly Flint letter corrects Norman Chesky's May 14 letter on Terry Teachout's article about Dave's True Story's latest recording0</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>We'd like to address Norman Chesky's letter of May 14 in response to Terry Teachout's article about Dave's True Story. In his letter, Mr. Chesky says it was ''financially unreasonable'' to rerecord our most recent record. He did not mention that Dave's True Story offered to pay for the two days of rerecording and adjustments we wished to make. Also, we were given the opportunity to rerecord several tracks on our first Chesky record, and these proved to be the most successful and popular tracks on the CD.</p>
        <p>DAVID CANTOR and KELLY FLINT  Manhattan</p>
      </block>
